@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ylpiei(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v1 + 0.99 * v0 + 0.97)))
    v2 = 0.45
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.sin(0.24))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.29 - v0 + 0.03)) / (0.23 + 0.08))
    v0 = (0.91 + wp.sin(v0))
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.04) / (tmp + 0.46 / v1 + 0.78)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
